ğŸ“¦ Installation
Clone the repository:
git clone https://github.com/your-username/US-States-Game.git
Navigate into the project directory:
cd US-States-Game
Install dependencies:
pip install pandas
turtle comes pre-installed with Python.
â–¶ï¸ How to Run
python main.py
Make sure all project files are in the same directory.
ğŸ® Gameplay Instructions
Enter the name of a US state in the input box.
Correct guesses appear on the map.
The score updates dynamically.
Type Exit to quit the game.
When exiting, a file called missing_state.csv is created with all unguessed states.
